{"word":"ἀφορία","slug":"ἀφορία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀφορία</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἄφορος'><el>ἄφορος</el></a>\n<p/><i>a not bearing</i>:<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>non-production, dearth</i>, <el>καρπῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>barrenness, sterility</i> of land: <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ἀφ. φρενῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}